item.title: CVE-2017-4942|2024-09-16T17:58:52.370Z -- vmware -- airwatch%20console
item.description: VMware AirWatch Console (AWC) contains a Broken Access Control vulnerability. Successful exploitation of this issue could result in end-user device details being disclosed to an unauthorized administrator.
